name: My Mind Palace (3/3)
description: Most of us have a happy place associated within our mind. A place that resonate good virtues, cozy life and everlasting purpose. An escape and resort.  I have been a creative for as long as I can remember. This is my first 3D rendered artwork which I did back in 2018. This is my happy place. An island close to my home, my mind.  My happy place.
